// Fikstür verileri oluşturma fonksiyonu
export const generateFixtures = (teams, leagueName) => {
  const fixtures = [];
  const teamNames = teams.map(team => team.name);

  // Her takımın diğer takımlarla ev sahibi ve deplasman maçı yapması
  for (let i = 0; i < teamNames.length; i++) {
    for (let j = i + 1; j < teamNames.length; j++) {
      // Ev sahibi maçı
      fixtures.push({
        homeTeam: teamNames[i],
        awayTeam: teamNames[j],
        homeScore: Math.floor(Math.random() * 4),
        awayScore: Math.floor(Math.random() * 4),
        matchday: Math.floor(Math.random() * 34) + 1,
        league: leagueName
      });

      // Deplasman maçı
      fixtures.push({
        homeTeam: teamNames[j],
        awayTeam: teamNames[i],
        homeScore: Math.floor(Math.random() * 4),
        awayScore: Math.floor(Math.random() * 4),
        matchday: Math.floor(Math.random() * 34) + 1,
        league: leagueName
      });
    }
  }
  return fixtures.sort((a, b) => a.matchday - b.matchday);
};

// Seçilen takım için varsayılan kulüp verisi
export const createClubData = (selectedTeam, leagueName) => {
  const team = turkishLeagues[leagueName].find(t => t.name === selectedTeam);
  return {
    name: selectedTeam,
    season: '2024/25',
    league: leagueName,
    date: 'Ağu 2024',
    hfSonu: Math.floor(Math.random() * 10) + 1,
    lig: team ? team.position : Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 1,
    money: Math.floor(team ? team.value * 1000000 : 5000000),
    kadro: Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 20,
    menajer: Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 30,
    antrenman: Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 30,
    altyapi: Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 30,
    kupalar: Math.floor(Math.random() * 5),
    basarildi: Math.floor(Math.random() * 10) + 1,
    taraftarMutlu: Math.floor(Math.random() * 30) + 70,
    baskanMutlu: Math.floor(Math.random() * 30) + 70,
    stadium: 'Stadyum',
    baskan: 'Başkan',
    matchResults: ['M', 'G', 'G', 'G', 'B', 'B'],
    nextMatch: `${leagueName}: ${turkishLeagues[leagueName][Math.floor(Math.random() * turkishLeagues[leagueName].length)].name} (D)`
  };
};

// Fikstür verileri oluşturma fonksiyonu
export const generateFixtures = (teams, leagueName) => {
  const fixtures = [];
  const teamNames = teams.map(team => team.name);
  
  // Her takımın diğer takımlarla ev sahibi ve deplasman maçı yapması
  for (let i = 0; i < teamNames.length; i++) {
    for (let j = i + 1; j < teamNames.length; j++) {
      // Ev sahibi maçı
      fixtures.push({
        homeTeam: teamNames[i],
        awayTeam: teamNames[j],
        homeScore: Math.floor(Math.random() * 4),
        awayScore: Math.floor(Math.random() * 4),
        matchday: Math.floor(Math.random() * 34) + 1,
        league: leagueName
      });
      
      // Deplasman maçı
      fixtures.push({
        homeTeam: teamNames[j],
        awayTeam: teamNames[i],
        homeScore: Math.floor(Math.random() * 4),
        awayScore: Math.floor(Math.random() * 4),
        matchday: Math.floor(Math.random() * 34) + 1,
        league: leagueName
      });
    }
  }
  
  return fixtures.sort((a, b) => a.matchday - b.matchday);
};

// Seçilen takım için varsayılan kulüp verisi
export const createClubData = (selectedTeam, leagueName) => {
  const team = turkishLeagues[leagueName].find(t => t.name === selectedTeam);
  
  return {
    name: selectedTeam,
    season: '2024/25',
    league: leagueName,
    date: 'Ağu 2024',
    hfSonu: Math.floor(Math.random() * 10) + 1,
    lig: team ? team.position : Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 1,
    money: Math.floor(team ? team.value * 1000000 : 5000000),
    kadro: Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 20,
    menajer: Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 30,
    antrenman: Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 30,
    altyapi: Math.floor(Math.random() * 20) + 30,
    kupalar: Math.floor(Math.random() * 5),
    basarildi: Math.floor(Math.random() * 10) + 1,
    taraftarMutlu: Math.floor(Math.random() * 30) + 70,
    baskanMutlu: Math.floor(Math.random() * 30) + 70,
    stadium: 'Stadyum',
    baskan: 'Başkan',
    matchResults: ['M', 'G', 'G', 'G', 'B', 'B'],
    nextMatch: `${leagueName}: ${turkishLeagues[leagueName][Math.floor(Math.random() * turkishLeagues[leagueName].length)].name} (D)`,
  };
};
